Package com.cba.worksubmission

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WorkItem
    WorkItem to be submitted to WorkItemExecutor for execution.
    WorkItemCompletionCallback
    A callback to consume result after WorkItem submission completed.
    WorkItemExecutor
    An Executor that provides methods to manage the threads executing the work item.
    WorkItemSubmissionResult
    The interface for receiving the submission result.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WorkItemCompletionCallbackImpl
    An implementation for a callback to consume result after WorkItem submission completed.
    WorkItemExecutorImpl
    An implementation of WorkItemExecutor that provides methods to manage the threads executing the work item.
    WorkItemImpl
    An implementation of a WorkItem to be submitted to WorkItemExecutor for execution.
    WorkItemSubmission
    The main class for running WorkItemSubmission.
    WorkItemSubmissionResultImpl
    An implementation of WorkItemSubmissionResult to provide status and message of WorkItem submission.
